item.title: By: Hyd
item.dc:creator: Hyd
item.description: It's a sad day for the U.S. edumacation system when not even one out of three of the best and brightest knows who Leeroy Jenkins is. Although I am a little surprised that the Jeopardy question writers _do_ know who he is.
item.content:encoded: It’s a sad day for the U.S. edumacation system when not even one out of three of the best and brightest knows who Leeroy Jenkins is. Although I am a little surprised that the Jeopardy question writers _do_ know who he is.
